OL,3,CThree teenagers sentenced after
OL,4,Ccausing 'serious fear' during disorder
OL,6,FThree teenagers who contributed to a
OL,7,F"general atmosphere of fear and
OL,8,Fdisorder" during the Plymouth disorder
OL,9,Fhave been sentenced for their
OL,10,Finvolvement.
OL,12,FThe boys, two aged 15 and one aged 17
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to violent disorder,
OL,14,Fafter taking part in the far-right
OL,15,Frally on Royal Parade on 5 August.
