OL,3,CThree teenagers sentenced after
OL,4,Ccausing 'serious fear' during disorder
OL,6,FEach of the three boys, who cannot be
OL,7,Fnamed because of their ages, were
OL,8,Fhanded 12-month referral orders,
OL,9,Finstead of a custodial sentence at
OL,10,FPlymouth Magistrates' Court on Monday
OL,11,F23 September.
OL,13,FThe judge concluded the boys would
OL,14,Fbenefit from intensive rehabilitation
OL,15,Factivities, with it being their first
OL,16,Fconviction.
OL,18,FIn court, CCTV footage was played
OL,19,Fshowing each of the boys' involvement,
OL,20,Fall three of them were caught throwing
OL,21,Fhard objects.
