OL,3,CThree teenagers sentenced after
OL,4,Ccausing 'serious fear' during disorder
OL,6,FThe first 15 year-old was shown
OL,7,Fthrowing a large brick which hit a
OL,8,Fpolice officer's shield.
OL,10,FThe second 15 year-old had been warned
OL,11,Fby his mother not to attend that
OL,12,Fevening. He ignored that advice and
OL,13,Fwas seen throwing rocks at counter
OL,14,Fprotestors.
OL,16,FBoth showed remorse and apologised for
OL,17,Ftheir involvement.
