OL,3,CThree teenagers sentenced after
OL,4,Ccausing 'serious fear' during disorder
OL,6,FThe 17 year-old was at the disorder
OL,7,Ffor three hours. Footage showed him
OL,8,Fthrowing rocks and a drinks can -after
OL,9,Fwhich he laughed and "fist bumped" his
OL,10,Ffriends.
OL,12,FJudge Smith said that despite their
OL,13,Factions not resulting in injuries, the
OL,14,Fboys "contributed to a general
OL,15,Fatmosphere of fear and disorder that
OL,16,Fwas racist and frightening to anyone
OL,17,Fwho was there".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
