OL,3,CThree teenagers sentenced after
OL,4,Ccausing 'serious fear' during disorder
OL,6,FHe added that across the country,
OL,7,Fadults who took part in the disorder
OL,8,Fhave been sentenced to anywhere
OL,9,Fbetween one and three years in prison.
OL,11,FThe judge added: "It was part of the
OL,12,Fwider national picture of civil
OL,13,Funrest, fuelled by misinformation and
OL,14,Fracist sentiment".
OL,16,FBy handing the three teenagers
OL,17,Freferral orders, the judge hoped it
OL,18,Fwould help them "make better choices
OL,19,Fin the future".
