OL,3,CThree teenagers sentenced after
OL,4,Ccausing 'serious fear' during disorder
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Dan Barter from
OL,7,FDevon and Cornwall Police said: "The
OL,8,Fevents that night caused serious fear
OL,9,Fin the community.
OL,11,F"We have seen dozens of people who
OL,12,Fwere intent on causing harm prosecuted
OL,13,Ffor their involvement. These boys
OL,14,Fcould have caused serious injury by
OL,15,Facting so recklessly and it is right
OL,16,Fthat they also faced justice."
